message.entry: Value must be a 1x2 vector of increasing datetime values.
Value must be a vector of increasing datetime values.
Datetime values in the ''UTCLeapSeconds'' time zone must have the standard leap second format.
Reference date must be at midnight.
Changing between a reference date with a time zone and one without a time zone is not supported.
Changing between a reference date with leap seconds and one without leap seconds is not supported.
Data inputs must match the axis configuration. Changing between datetime data with a time zone and data without a time zone is not supported.
Data inputs must match the axis configuration. Changing between datetime data with leap seconds and data without leap seconds is not supported.
Value to convert must be a numeric or datetime array.
